1
00:00:07,834 --> 00:00:09,000
- EARTH.

2
00:00:09,041 --> 00:00:10,875
FIRE.

3
00:00:10,917 --> 00:00:12,625
AIR.

4
00:00:12,667 --> 00:00:14,792
WATER.

5
00:00:14,834 --> 00:00:18,834
ONLY THE AVATAR CAN MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

6
00:00:18,875 --> 00:00:21,500
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

7
00:00:21,542 --> 00:00:24,000
[epic music]

8
00:00:24,041 --> 00:00:25,542
♪ ♪

9
00:00:27,208 --> 00:00:28,875
- AIRBENDERS ARE
MYSTERIOUSLY DISAPPEARING

10
00:00:28,917 --> 00:00:30,834
IN BA SING SE,
INCLUDING KAI.

11
00:00:30,875 --> 00:00:33,250
THE EARTH QUEEN DENIED
ANY KNOWLEDGE OF THE AIRBENDERS,

12
00:00:33,291 --> 00:00:35,250
BUT KORRA REFUSED
TO GIVE UP HER SEARCH.

13
00:00:35,291 --> 00:00:37,792
MEANWHILE, MAKO AND BOLIN
MET THEIR LONG-LOST RELATIVES,

14
00:00:37,834 --> 00:00:39,542
WHO TOLD THEM
THAT DAI LI AGENTS

15
00:00:39,583 --> 00:00:41,667
HAVE BEEN ROUNDING UP AIRBENDERS
FOR THE QUEEN'S ARMY.

16
00:00:41,709 --> 00:00:43,250
AND AT A PRISON
IN THE NORTH,

17
00:00:43,291 --> 00:00:46,291
TONRAQ AND LORD ZUKO PREPARE
FOR ZAHEER'S IMMINENT ATTACK.

18
00:00:51,667 --> 00:00:54,625
[suspenseful music]

19
00:00:54,667 --> 00:01:02,417
♪ ♪

20
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:08,291
[dragon shrieks]

21
00:01:12,333 --> 00:01:14,291
- DID YOU SEE ZAHEER?

22
00:01:14,333 --> 00:01:17,417
- THE ONLY THING I SAW
WAS A SNOWSTORM HEADING OUR WAY.

23
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,917
- THAT'S NOT A SNOWSTORM.
THAT'S HIM.

24
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:27,917
[dramatic music]

25
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:35,625
♪ ♪

26
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:53,041
I PUT YOU AWAY ONCE, ZAHEER,
AND I'M GOING TO DO IT AGAIN.

27
00:01:53,083 --> 00:01:55,333
[yells]

28
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,875
- [grunts]

29
00:02:46,667 --> 00:02:48,375
- MING-HUA.

30
00:02:48,417 --> 00:02:51,458
- LET'S GET YOU OUT OF HERE.

31
00:03:07,041 --> 00:03:10,917
- WE COULD HAVE JUST TAKEN
THE ELEVATOR, SHOW-OFF.

32
00:03:14,625 --> 00:03:15,917
[dragon shrieks]

33
00:03:25,834 --> 00:03:30,333
I'VE WAITED 13 YEARS
TO FEEL THIS WARM.

34
00:03:33,417 --> 00:03:34,709
[dragon shrieks]

35
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,291
- [yells]

36
00:03:54,083 --> 00:03:56,083
[engine starts]

37
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:03,083
- I THOUGHT
I'D NEVER SEE YOU AGAIN.

38
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:05,458
- I NEVER DOUBTED.

39
00:04:08,041 --> 00:04:10,625
- REALLY? RIGHT NOW?

40
00:04:17,250 --> 00:04:18,917
- I GOT 'EM!

41
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:21,125
THESE PASSPORTS SHOULD GET YOU
INTO THE UPPER RING.

42
00:04:21,166 --> 00:04:25,583
- AWESOME! TU, YOU'RE THE BEST
COUSIN A GUY COULD HAVE.

43
00:04:25,625 --> 00:04:28,000
AND MY OTHER COUSINS
AS WELL.

44
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:30,792
YEAH.
YEAH, YOU'RE ALL THE BEST.

45
00:04:30,834 --> 00:04:34,125
- THANKS.
I KNOW THIS WASN'T EASY.

46
00:04:34,166 --> 00:04:37,208
- IT'S SUCH A SHAME
YOU TWO MUST LEAVE SO SOON.

47
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,667
- I WISH WE COULD STAY.

48
00:04:38,709 --> 00:04:40,375
BUT IF IT'S TRUE
THE EARTH QUEEN

49
00:04:40,417 --> 00:04:42,583
IS FORCING AIRBENDERS
INTO HER ARMY,

50
00:04:42,625 --> 00:04:44,291
WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING
ABOUT IT.

51
00:04:44,333 --> 00:04:47,667
- I LOVE YOU BOTH.
COME VISIT AGAIN.

52
00:04:47,709 --> 00:04:49,417
- WE WILL, GRANDMA.

53
00:04:49,458 --> 00:04:51,834
- I LOVE YOU TOO, GRANDMA.

54
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:55,625
AND CHOW AND TU

55
00:04:55,667 --> 00:04:58,333
AND MENG-MENG
AND CHOW JR.

56
00:04:58,375 --> 00:05:01,792
AND THERE HE IS,
BIG TEE AND LITTLE--LITTLE TEE,

57
00:05:01,834 --> 00:05:05,500
AND MEDIUM YU AND--AND--
AND WHAT WAS YOUR NAME AGAIN?

58
00:05:05,542 --> 00:05:08,000
- [grunting]

59
00:05:08,041 --> 00:05:10,375
I KNOW THAT EARTH QUEEN
IS LYING TO ME.

60
00:05:10,417 --> 00:05:13,792
I CAN TELL BY THAT STUPID
LITTLE QUEENY SMIRK OF HERS!

61
00:05:13,834 --> 00:05:15,709
AND I CAN'T BELIEVE
I HELPED HER.

62
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:18,250
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
SHE WAS USING ME!

63
00:05:18,291 --> 00:05:19,500
[grunts]

64
00:05:19,542 --> 00:05:21,166
- WHOA! HEY!

65
00:05:21,208 --> 00:05:22,583
I THINK I COULD USE A BREAK.

66
00:05:22,625 --> 00:05:24,792
YOU LETTING OFF STEAM
IS STARTING TO...

67
00:05:24,834 --> 00:05:26,500
HURT...A LOT.

68
00:05:26,542 --> 00:05:27,709
- SORRY.

69
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:29,125
[Pabu chittering]

70
00:05:29,166 --> 00:05:30,792
MAKO! BOLIN!

71
00:05:30,834 --> 00:05:32,375
[both panting]
YOU'RE OKAY.

72
00:05:32,417 --> 00:05:33,875
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

73
00:05:36,667 --> 00:05:37,959
- WE CHASED KAI...

74
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,917
TRAIN...
SLIPPED AWAY...

75
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:42,333
LOWER RING...
SLEPT IN TRASH PILE...

76
00:05:42,375 --> 00:05:43,792
MET OUR FAMILY...

77
00:05:43,834 --> 00:05:46,208
GRANDMA, TEARS...
MAKO SCARF...

78
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:48,834
EARTH QUEEN LYING.

79
00:05:48,875 --> 00:05:50,458
MM.

80
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:52,000
- CAN YOU INTERPRET THAT?

81
00:05:52,041 --> 00:05:54,417
- THE EARTH QUEEN'S BEEN
SECRETLY TAKING AIRBENDERS

82
00:05:54,458 --> 00:05:56,333
AND FORCING THEM
INTO HER ARMY.

83
00:05:56,375 --> 00:05:59,583
- SHE WAS LYING.
I KNEW IT!

84
00:05:59,625 --> 00:06:01,500
I SWEAR,
THE NEXT TIME I SEE HER...

85
00:06:01,542 --> 00:06:03,375
- IT'S THE QUEEN.

86
00:06:06,917 --> 00:06:10,291
- QUICK, PABU, SHIRT!
[Pabu chittering]

87
00:06:10,333 --> 00:06:13,000
I KNOW. SORRY.
KINDA SWEATY.

88
00:06:14,667 --> 00:06:17,917
- GOOD, YOU'RE HERE.
GUN, TELL HER THE NEWS.

89
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:20,458
- WE'VE RECEIVED WORD
FROM THE YANG PROVINCE.

90
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:22,583
THERE HAVE BEEN REPORTS
OF AIRBENDERS THERE.

91
00:06:22,625 --> 00:06:24,625
- WONDERFUL, ISN'T IT?

92
00:06:24,667 --> 00:06:26,417
IT'S THE VERY THING
YOU'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR.

93
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:28,500
- THANK YOU.

94
00:06:28,542 --> 00:06:31,667
THAT IS JUST
THE MOST WONDERFUL NEWS, EVER.

95
00:06:31,709 --> 00:06:33,041
YAY.

96
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:37,583
- SO I ASSUME YOU AND YOUR...
FRIENDS HERE

97
00:06:37,625 --> 00:06:39,208
WILL BE LEAVING IMMEDIATELY.

98
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:42,000
AHHH, AH-CHOO!

99
00:06:42,041 --> 00:06:43,667
AH-CHOO!

100
00:06:43,709 --> 00:06:45,542
AHHHH, AH-CHOO!

101
00:06:45,583 --> 00:06:49,667
IS THERE AN ANIMAL
IN MY PRESENCE?

102
00:06:49,709 --> 00:06:51,083
- NO, YOUR MAJESTY.

103
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:53,458
I WOULD NEVER ALLOW
AN ANIMAL NEAR YOU.

104
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:57,542
- AH-CHOO!
AHH, AHH, AH-CHOO!

105
00:06:57,583 --> 00:07:03,125
IF I FIND ONE WITHIN 50 FEET
OF ME, IT'S YOUR HEAD!

106
00:07:03,166 --> 00:07:06,709
ANYWAY, IF YOU NEED
ANY ASSISTANCE PACKING,

107
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:08,333
LET GUN KNOW.

108
00:07:08,375 --> 00:07:11,291
HE'LL SEE TO IT THAT YOU ARE
ON YOUR WAY BY EVENING.

109
00:07:11,333 --> 00:07:13,875
- UH, THIS EVENING?

110
00:07:13,917 --> 00:07:16,125
I'M NOT SURE
ABOUT LEAVING SO SOON.

111
00:07:16,166 --> 00:07:18,417
- BECAUSE OUR AIRSHIP
IS HAVING ENGINE TROUBLE.

112
00:07:18,458 --> 00:07:20,875
IT'LL TAKE ME UNTIL TOMORROW
TO FINISH THE REPAIRS.

113
00:07:20,917 --> 00:07:25,875
- AHH, AHH, AH-CHOO!
AH-CHOO!

114
00:07:25,917 --> 00:07:27,375
AH-CHOO!

115
00:07:27,417 --> 00:07:30,709
- THANKS FOR BUYING US
SOME TIME.

116
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,583
- I CAN'T BELIEVE
THE EARTH QUEEN

117
00:07:32,625 --> 00:07:34,166
IS CONSCRIPTING AIRBENDERS.

118
00:07:34,208 --> 00:07:36,709
- THOSE PEOPLE SHOULD NOT
BE FORCED TO JOIN AN ARMY.

119
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:38,333
- WELL, TECHNICALLY,

120
00:07:38,375 --> 00:07:41,917
THE EARTH QUEEN HAS A RIGHT
TO CONSCRIPT HER CITIZENS.

121
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,709
WHAT?
IT'S TRUE.

122
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:46,166
- GUYS, WHAT IF KAI
WAS SPOTTED AIRBENDING?

123
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:47,750
HE MIGHT HAVE BEEN
TAKEN TOO.

124
00:07:47,792 --> 00:07:49,125
- PROBABLY NOT.

125
00:07:49,166 --> 00:07:50,834
HE'S SURPRISINGLY DIFFICULT
TO CATCH.

126
00:07:50,875 --> 00:07:53,291
LIKE A--LIKE A LITTLE
GREASED HOG-MONKEY.

127
00:07:53,333 --> 00:07:55,709
- BUT WHAT IF HE WAS?

128
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:58,250
- DON'T WORRY, JINORA.
WE'LL FIND HIM.

129
00:07:58,291 --> 00:08:00,417
WE JUST NEED TO FIGURE OUT
WHERE TO LOOK.

130
00:08:00,458 --> 00:08:03,834
- I BET
THEY'RE UNDER LAKE LAOGAI.

131
00:08:03,875 --> 00:08:07,041
WHAT? I'VE BEEN READING
SOME OF JINORA'S BOOKS.

132
00:08:07,083 --> 00:08:09,333
THE OLD DAI LI AGENTS
USED TO HAVE A SECRET FORTRESS

133
00:08:09,375 --> 00:08:10,875
BENEATH THE LAKE.

134
00:08:10,917 --> 00:08:12,333
- MAKO'S RIGHT.

135
00:08:12,375 --> 00:08:14,041
IT'S THE PERFECT SPOT
TO HIDE AIRBENDERS.

136
00:08:14,083 --> 00:08:16,709
AND I KNOW HOW TO CHECK IT OUT
WITHOUT BEING CAUGHT.

137
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:19,000
I CAN PROJECT MY SPIRIT
INTO IT.

138
00:08:19,041 --> 00:08:21,250
- YOU MEAN
THAT OUT-OF-BODY THING YOU DID

139
00:08:21,291 --> 00:08:22,542
TO HELP GIANT SPIRITY-KORRA?

140
00:08:22,583 --> 00:08:24,333
- YOU CAN STILL DO THAT?

141
00:08:24,375 --> 00:08:28,000
- IT'S NOT AS POWERFUL AS IT WAS
DURING HARMONIC CONVERGENCE,

142
00:08:28,041 --> 00:08:31,125
BUT IF I CAN GET CLOSE ENOUGH,
I THINK I CAN DO IT.

143
00:08:31,166 --> 00:08:32,583
- LET'S GO GET KAI OUT.

144
00:08:32,625 --> 00:08:34,500
LET'S GET
ALL THE AIRBENDERS OUT.

145
00:08:41,208 --> 00:08:43,500
- YOU ARE THE PROPERTY
OF THE EARTH KINGDOM.

146
00:08:43,542 --> 00:08:46,375
YOU WILL BECOME THE EARTH
QUEEN'S ELITE FIGHTING FORCE

147
00:08:46,417 --> 00:08:48,041
AND PROTECT HER AT ALL COST.

148
00:08:48,083 --> 00:08:51,583
IT IS YOUR DUTY
TO SERVE THE EARTH QUEEN.

149
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:59,625
- AAH!

150
00:08:59,667 --> 00:09:02,125
- GO EASY ON ME.

151
00:09:02,166 --> 00:09:04,834
I'M NOT THAT GOOD.

152
00:09:09,166 --> 00:09:10,709
- NEVER SHOW MERCY!

153
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,166
NOW ATTACK YOUR OPPONENT,

154
00:09:12,208 --> 00:09:15,125
AND THIS TIME,
LIKE YOU MEAN IT.

155
00:09:15,166 --> 00:09:18,166
- [grunting]

156
00:09:18,208 --> 00:09:19,834
- SORRY.

157
00:09:19,875 --> 00:09:21,625
- A SOLDIER NEVER APOLOGIZES
TO HIS ENEMY.

158
00:09:21,667 --> 00:09:23,083
- I'M NOT A SOLDIER.

159
00:09:23,125 --> 00:09:26,041
- YOU WILL BE
WHEN I'M THROUGH WITH YOU.

160
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,417
[Oogi growling]

161
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:37,583
- IF ANYTHING GOES WRONG,
COME BACK IMMEDIATELY.

162
00:09:37,625 --> 00:09:40,500
- I WILL.

163
00:10:15,792 --> 00:10:18,458
- WHAT HAPPENED?
WHAT DID YOU SEE?

164
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,959
- THE AIRBENDERS AREN'T THERE.
IT'S COMPLETELY DESERTED.

165
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,041
- THEY'RE NOT DOWN THERE?

166
00:10:24,083 --> 00:10:26,166
- JINORA, YOU'VE READ
ALL ABOUT BA SING SE.

167
00:10:26,208 --> 00:10:27,542
CAN YOU THINK
OF ANY OTHER PLACES

168
00:10:27,583 --> 00:10:28,834
THE AIRBENDERS MIGHT BE?

169
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:30,709
- I GUESS THEY COULD BE
IN THE CATACOMBS

170
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:32,417
BENEATH THE UPPER RING

171
00:10:32,458 --> 00:10:34,834
OR THE ANCIENT SEWERS
BENEATH THE LOWER RING

172
00:10:34,875 --> 00:10:38,417
OR THE MAZE OF TUNNELS THAT
CONNECTS THE RINGS TOGETHER,

173
00:10:38,458 --> 00:10:39,917
OR THEY COULD BE--
- [sighs]

174
00:10:39,959 --> 00:10:41,417
THERE ARE
JUST TOO MANY PLACES.

175
00:10:41,458 --> 00:10:42,959
THERE HAS TO BE
ANOTHER WAY TO LOCATE THEM.

176
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,458
- MAYBE THERE IS.

177
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,041
HOW DID YOU FIND ME
DURING HARMONIC CONVERGENCE?

178
00:10:46,083 --> 00:10:47,500
- I DON'T KNOW.

179
00:10:47,542 --> 00:10:50,375
I JUST KIND OF FOCUSED
ON YOUR ENERGY.

180
00:10:50,417 --> 00:10:53,000
I THINK OUR SPIRITUAL CONNECTION
LED ME TO YOU.

181
00:10:53,041 --> 00:10:55,375
- MAYBE YOU CAN FIND KAI
THE SAME WAY.

182
00:10:55,417 --> 00:10:57,500
I KNOW YOU TWO
HAVE A CONNECTION.

183
00:10:57,542 --> 00:10:59,542
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN
A CONNECTION?

184
00:10:59,583 --> 00:11:04,166
- I DON'T KNOW.
LET ME TRY.

185
00:11:04,208 --> 00:11:06,917
[serene music]

186
00:11:06,959 --> 00:11:14,875
♪ ♪

187
00:11:18,875 --> 00:11:20,542
- UGH!

188
00:11:20,583 --> 00:11:22,959
- [grunts]

189
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
- UGH!

190
00:11:25,041 --> 00:11:26,375
[disk shatters]

191
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:31,250
- [whimpers]
[disk shatters]

192
00:11:31,291 --> 00:11:33,709
THANKS.
- YOU AGAIN!

193
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,500
IF YOU HAVE TIME
TO HELP YOUR FRIEND,

194
00:11:35,542 --> 00:11:38,375
MAYBE YOU'RE NOT GETTING
ENOUGH ROCKS FOR YOURSELF.

195
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:44,834
[disks shattering]

196
00:11:44,875 --> 00:11:47,417
- [grunting]

197
00:11:51,917 --> 00:11:55,166
- I GUESS YOU'RE NOT
AS GOOD AS YOU THOUGHT.

198
00:11:59,291 --> 00:12:01,667
THROW HIM IN THE HOLE!

199
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,542
- [grunts]

200
00:12:17,041 --> 00:12:18,375
[screams]

201
00:12:19,875 --> 00:12:22,458
JINORA?
- IT WORKED!

202
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:24,375
- HOW ARE YOU HERE
RIGHT NOW?

203
00:12:24,417 --> 00:12:26,500
- SHH, QUIET.

204
00:12:26,542 --> 00:12:28,291
IT'S A HIGH-LEVEL
AIRBENDER MOVE...

205
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:30,041
WITH A LITTLE SPIRITUAL STUFF
THROWN IN.

206
00:12:30,083 --> 00:12:31,792
- [sighs]

207
00:12:31,834 --> 00:12:34,250
FOR A SECOND THERE,
I THOUGHT YOU WERE A GHOST.

208
00:12:34,291 --> 00:12:35,959
- [giggles]
IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU.

209
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,250
WE'VE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU
AND THE OTHER AIRBENDERS.

210
00:12:38,291 --> 00:12:40,166
WE'RE GOING TO GET YOU ALL
OUT OF HERE.

211
00:12:40,208 --> 00:12:41,834
WHERE ARE WE ANYWAY?

212
00:12:41,875 --> 00:12:43,792
- UNDERGROUND SOMEWHERE.

213
00:12:43,834 --> 00:12:45,709
OTHER THAN THAT,
I DON'T HAVE A CLUE.

214
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:48,041
- I'LL FIGURE IT OUT.
DON'T WORRY.

215
00:12:48,083 --> 00:12:50,625
- JINORA...
THANKS.

216
00:13:02,917 --> 00:13:05,875
- THE EARTH QUEEN'S TEMPLE.

217
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,834
- I CAN'T BELIEVE
MISS QUEENY SMUGFACE

218
00:13:09,875 --> 00:13:11,834
HAD THEM RIGHT UNDER OUR NOSES
THE WHOLE TIME!

219
00:13:11,875 --> 00:13:14,375
- WE HAVE TO GET
INTO THAT COMPOUND TONIGHT

220
00:13:14,417 --> 00:13:16,083
AND GET THOSE AIRBENDERS OUT.

221
00:13:16,125 --> 00:13:18,125
- ALL RIGHT, WE GO IN
UNDER THE COVER OF DARKNESS.

222
00:13:18,166 --> 00:13:21,041
TWO SMALL INSERTION TEAMS
AND A THIRD ON THE OUTSIDE.

223
00:13:21,083 --> 00:13:24,291
THEN ALL WE'LL NEED
IS 12 TONS OF BLASTING JELLY,

224
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:26,375
A MEDIUM-SIZED BULLDOZER
AND...

225
00:13:26,417 --> 00:13:28,625
DOES ANYONE HAVE A BADGER-MOLE
THAT KNOWS MORSE CODE?

226
00:13:28,667 --> 00:13:31,291
- [sighs]
[knock on door]

227
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:33,166
- OH, GREAT.
NOT THE QUEEN AGAIN.

228
00:13:33,208 --> 00:13:35,625
- EVERYONE ACT NORMAL.
AND, BOLIN--

229
00:13:35,667 --> 00:13:37,458
- I'M ON IT!

230
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,875
[Pabu chittering]

231
00:13:38,917 --> 00:13:40,166
WHAT?

232
00:13:40,208 --> 00:13:43,583
HEY, I'M NOT SWEATY
THIS TIME.

233
00:13:46,375 --> 00:13:48,500
AH!

234
00:13:52,041 --> 00:13:55,208
- LIN?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

235
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:57,625
- WE NEED TO GET KORRA
OUT OF HERE IMMEDIATELY.

236
00:13:57,667 --> 00:13:59,041
HER LIFE'S IN DANGER.
- WHAT?

237
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:01,208
WHAT'S GOING ON?

238
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:03,375
- I JUST GOT WORD FROM LORD ZUKO
AND TONRAQ.

239
00:14:03,417 --> 00:14:05,583
- WHY IS LORD ZUKO
WITH MY DAD?

240
00:14:05,625 --> 00:14:07,166
- ZAHEER AND THE OTHERS
HAVE ESCAPED.

241
00:14:07,208 --> 00:14:09,500
- HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?

242
00:14:09,542 --> 00:14:11,625
- BECAUSE ZAHEER
IS AN AIRBENDER NOW.

243
00:14:11,667 --> 00:14:12,792
- NO.

244
00:14:12,834 --> 00:14:15,291
- ALL RIGHT, HOLD ON.

245
00:14:15,333 --> 00:14:17,959
WILL YOU QUIT IGNORING ME
AND TELL ME WHAT'S GOING ON?

246
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:21,000
WHO'S ZAHEER?
WHY IS MY LIFE IN DANGER?

247
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:26,041
- SHORTLY AFTER WE FOUND OUT
YOU WERE THE AVATAR,

248
00:14:26,083 --> 00:14:29,083
ZAHEER AND THREE OTHERS
ATTEMPTED TO KIDNAP YOU.

249
00:14:29,125 --> 00:14:31,750
LUCKILY, YOUR FATHER,
LORD ZUKO, CHIEF SOKKA, AND I

250
00:14:31,792 --> 00:14:33,417
WERE THERE TO STOP THEM.

251
00:14:33,458 --> 00:14:36,000
WE APPREHENDED THE CRIMINALS
AND LOCKED THEM AWAY IN PRISONS

252
00:14:36,041 --> 00:14:38,041
DESIGNED TO IMPAIR
THEIR ABILITIES.

253
00:14:38,083 --> 00:14:40,500
- SO THAT'S WHY YOU AND MY DAD
SHELTERED ME AWAY.

254
00:14:40,542 --> 00:14:42,917
- IT WAS FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY.

255
00:14:42,959 --> 00:14:44,959
- WHY WERE THEY TRYING
TO KIDNAP KORRA?

256
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,375
- WE SPENT 13 YEARS
INTERROGATING THEM,

257
00:14:47,417 --> 00:14:48,917
BUT THEY NEVER BROKE.

258
00:14:48,959 --> 00:14:51,166
TO THIS DAY, NO ONE KNOWS
WHAT THEIR MOTIVE WAS.

259
00:14:51,208 --> 00:14:52,917
NOW WE NEED TO GET YOU BACK
TO REPUBLIC CITY,

260
00:14:52,959 --> 00:14:54,417
WHERE I CAN PROTECT YOU.

261
00:14:54,458 --> 00:14:56,583
- NO, I'M NOT RUNNING.

262
00:14:56,625 --> 00:14:58,792
- KORRA,
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

263
00:14:58,834 --> 00:15:01,500
THESE CRIMINALS ARE LIKE NOTHING
YOU'VE EVER FACED BEFORE.

264
00:15:01,542 --> 00:15:04,250
- LOOK, I'M NOT
A LITTLE KID ANYMORE.

265
00:15:04,291 --> 00:15:06,250
YOU DON'T NEED TO PROTECT ME.

266
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:08,250
I CAME HERE FOR ONE THING--
TO FIND AIRBENDERS--

267
00:15:08,291 --> 00:15:09,792
AND I'M NOT LEAVING
WITHOUT THEM.

268
00:15:09,834 --> 00:15:11,417
- FINE, LET'S GET 'EM
AND GET OUT OF HERE.

269
00:15:11,458 --> 00:15:12,750
WHERE ARE THEY?

270
00:15:12,792 --> 00:15:14,917
- IN A MILITARY COMPOUND,

271
00:15:14,959 --> 00:15:16,500
AND WE'RE BUSTING THEM OUT.

272
00:15:25,625 --> 00:15:27,750
- HI.
- HEY! WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

273
00:15:27,792 --> 00:15:29,542
- AW, IT'S JUST
THAT LITTLE AIRBENDER GIRL

274
00:15:29,583 --> 00:15:31,000
WHO CAME WITH THE AVATAR.

275
00:15:31,041 --> 00:15:33,083
YOU SHOULDN'T BE WALKING
AROUND HERE ALL ALONE.

276
00:15:33,125 --> 00:15:36,166
- I'M NOT ALONE.

277
00:15:58,208 --> 00:15:59,625
- BUMI AND KORRA,

278
00:15:59,667 --> 00:16:01,417
YOU TWO WILL COME WITH ME
TO FIND THE AIRBENDERS.

279
00:16:01,458 --> 00:16:03,959
YOU THREE FIND KAI.

280
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,458
WE'LL MEET
ON THE SURFACE SHORTLY.

281
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:07,500
RADIO US
IF ANYTHING GOES WRONG.

282
00:16:17,041 --> 00:16:20,166
- WHAT'S GOING ON?
WHO ARE YOU?

283
00:16:20,208 --> 00:16:21,667
- I'M THE AVATAR,

284
00:16:21,709 --> 00:16:23,291
AND I'M GETTING YOU ALL
OUT OF HERE.

285
00:16:23,333 --> 00:16:25,542
- WE'RE LEAVING?
- WHERE ARE WE GOING?

286
00:16:25,583 --> 00:16:31,458
- EVERYONE, PLEASE,
YOU MUST STAY CALM AND QUIET
IF WE WANT THIS TO WORK.
- WHAT TO WORK?

287
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:32,542
WE'RE SNEAKING OUT?

288
00:16:32,583 --> 00:16:34,917
- YES,
AND WE MUST LEAVE NOW.

289
00:16:34,959 --> 00:16:39,000
- WE'RE GOING TO GET YOU
AWAY FROM THE EARTH QUEEN
AND OUT OF THE CITY.

290
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:42,667
- THERE'S AN AIRBENDER
THAT'S NOT HERE.

291
00:16:42,709 --> 00:16:45,792
HIS NAME IS KAI.
WE NEED TO GET HIM.

292
00:16:45,834 --> 00:16:47,375
- WE'RE ALREADY
TAKING CARE OF IT.

293
00:16:47,417 --> 00:16:50,208
- TOPSIDE, THIS IS PAPA BEAR.
THE BREEZIES ARE IN THE HOLD.

294
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:51,208
CUE THE BALLOONS.

295
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:52,291
[radio static]
- WHAT?

296
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:53,917
ARE YOU IN TROUBLE?
- NO!

297
00:16:53,959 --> 00:16:55,792
WE GOT THE AIRBENDERS,
AND WE'RE HEADED OUT.

298
00:16:55,834 --> 00:16:57,625
BRING THE AIRSHIPS.

299
00:16:57,667 --> 00:17:00,291
NO ONE LIKES CODE NAMES
ANYMORE.

300
00:17:00,333 --> 00:17:03,542
- COPY THAT.
ASAMI AND I ARE ON OUR WAY.

301
00:17:08,041 --> 00:17:09,417
[Oogi growls]

302
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:13,959
- COME ON,
WE'RE GETTING YOU OUT.

303
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,417
- KAI!

304
00:17:17,792 --> 00:17:19,500
MWAH!

305
00:17:19,542 --> 00:17:21,750
- WHOA!

306
00:17:21,792 --> 00:17:24,041
TENZIN'S NOT GOING
TO BE HAPPY ABOUT THIS.

307
00:17:24,083 --> 00:17:25,458
- THEN DON'T TELL HIM.

308
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:27,667
- HOW CAN I NOT?
THIS IS TOO JUICY!

309
00:17:27,709 --> 00:17:29,375
- THANKS FOR COMING
TO GET ME.

310
00:17:29,417 --> 00:17:31,667
I'M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT STEALING YOUR WALLETS

311
00:17:31,709 --> 00:17:33,000
AND RUNNING AWAY

312
00:17:33,041 --> 00:17:36,000
AND GETTING YOU STUCK
ON THAT TRAIN.

313
00:17:36,041 --> 00:17:39,000
- OH, WE CAN'T STAY MAD
AT YOU!

314
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:40,667
- YES, WE CAN.

315
00:17:40,709 --> 00:17:42,041
I HAD A LOT OF MONEY
IN THAT WALLET!

316
00:17:42,083 --> 00:17:43,625
- GUYS, COME ON.

317
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:50,375
- DESERTING HER MAJESTY'S ARMY
IS HIGH TREASON,

318
00:17:50,417 --> 00:17:52,834
PUNISHABLE BY DEATH.

319
00:18:00,291 --> 00:18:03,417
- COME ON, IT'S CLEAR.

320
00:18:11,667 --> 00:18:13,917
- SO YOU'VE DISCOVERED
MY ELITE ARMY.

321
00:18:13,959 --> 00:18:17,208
I SEE THEIR LOYALTY
STILL NEEDS SOME WORK.

322
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:19,917
- THESE AIRBENDERS
SHOULDN'T BE USED AS WEAPONS.

323
00:18:19,959 --> 00:18:21,500
THEY HAVE A RIGHT TO CHOOSE
THEIR OWN PATHS.

324
00:18:21,542 --> 00:18:25,250
- THESE AIRBENDERS
ARE EARTH KINGDOM CITIZENS,

325
00:18:25,291 --> 00:18:27,083
AND I AM THEIR QUEEN.

326
00:18:27,125 --> 00:18:29,625
TAKING THEM WILL CONSTITUTE
AN ACT OF WAR.

327
00:18:29,667 --> 00:18:34,250
IF YOU DISOBEY ME,
I WILL BEAR DOWN ON YOU

328
00:18:34,291 --> 00:18:36,375
WITH THE ENTIRE FORCE
OF MY KINGDOM!

329
00:18:36,417 --> 00:18:38,875
- THEY'RE LEAVING WITH ME.

330
00:18:38,917 --> 00:18:41,375
- NO, THEY'RE NOT!

331
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:59,250
[airship approaching]

332
00:19:01,792 --> 00:19:02,750
- COME ON!

333
00:19:09,125 --> 00:19:12,083
[thrilling music]

334
00:19:12,125 --> 00:19:14,750
♪ ♪

335
00:19:14,792 --> 00:19:16,667
- [yells]

336
00:19:26,166 --> 00:19:28,834
- [screams]

337
00:19:36,083 --> 00:19:40,083
- [groans]

338
00:19:40,125 --> 00:19:42,458
- I GUESS I AM AS GOOD
AS I THOUGHT.

339
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,959
[radio static]
- EVERYONE'S IN. LET'S GO!

340
00:19:49,125 --> 00:19:52,166
- [yells]

341
00:19:57,417 --> 00:19:59,834
- [whistles]
OOGI!

342
00:19:59,875 --> 00:20:02,417
[Oogi growls]

343
00:20:06,875 --> 00:20:08,709
- TAKE DOWN THOSE AIRSHIPS!

344
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:13,917
- WHERE ARE THE OTHERS?

345
00:20:13,959 --> 00:20:17,750
- WE NEED<i> HELP!</i>

346
00:20:30,250 --> 00:20:32,417
EVERYBODY, HANG ON!

347
00:20:32,458 --> 00:20:34,375
[all screaming]

348
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:40,959
- WHOA, THAT WAS AWESOME!
- [grunts]

349
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,458
- BRING ME
THOSE AIRSHIPS NOW!

350
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:45,458
AHH, AH-CHOO!

351
00:20:45,500 --> 00:20:48,208
OH, GET IT OFF ME!
AH-CHOO!

352
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:52,291
GET THIS FUR OFF--
AHHH-CHOO!

353
00:20:59,125 --> 00:21:02,166
- I KNOW THAT NONE OF YOU
CHOSE TO BECOME AIRBENDERS,

354
00:21:02,208 --> 00:21:05,000
BUT NOW YOU DO
HAVE A CHOICE.

355
00:21:05,041 --> 00:21:07,709
WE CAN RELOCATE YOU
SOMEWHERE SAFE,

356
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:10,750
OR YOU CAN COME WITH ME
TO THE NORTHERN AIR TEMPLE

357
00:21:10,792 --> 00:21:14,250
TO LIVE IN PEACE
AND TRAIN AS AIR NOMADS.

358
00:21:14,291 --> 00:21:16,667
YOU ARE NO LONGER
ANYONE'S PROPERTY.

359
00:21:16,709 --> 00:21:20,542
WHAT PATH YOU DECIDE
IS UP TO YOU.

360
00:21:22,542 --> 00:21:24,667
- I WANT TO GO WITH YOU.

361
00:21:24,709 --> 00:21:26,875
- ME TOO.
- COUNT ME IN.

362
00:21:26,917 --> 00:21:29,291
- I WANNA GO TOO.
- I'LL GO TOO.
- ME TOO.
- SOUNDS LIKE FUN.

363
00:21:29,333 --> 00:21:30,834
- I WANNA GO TOO.
- OOH, I WANNA GO.

364
00:21:34,417 --> 00:21:36,375
- GOOD LUCK
AT THE NORTHERN AIR TEMPLE.

365
00:21:36,417 --> 00:21:39,083
I'LL SEND MORE AIRBENDERS
YOUR WAY WHEN I FIND THEM.

366
00:21:39,125 --> 00:21:43,250
- BE CAREFUL OUT THERE,
AND STAY SAFE.
- I'LL TRY.

367
00:21:43,291 --> 00:21:46,041
IT SEEMS LIKE WHEREVER I GO,
I MAKE A NEW ENEMY.

368
00:21:46,083 --> 00:21:48,500
- BUT YOU MADE
SOME NEW FRIENDS TOO.

369
00:21:48,542 --> 00:21:51,917
YOU DID WELL, KORRA.

370
00:21:51,959 --> 00:21:53,750
- THIS IS
ONLY THE BEGINNING.
